# nyxloom-trove — what NOT to commit by default.
#
# Agent logs: per-attempt transcripts (spec.json, receipt.json, attempt.log).
# Kept in the repo for locality, but NOT committed by default (churny,
# regenerable). To keep FULL traceability, delete the line below (or force-add
# specific runs: `git add -f agent-logs/<att-id>`).
agent-logs/
